# Private hackathon strategy docs — kept out of the public repo until
# after the event (rival teams should not read the pitch script, judge-
# Q&A prep, or weakness analysis). Can be flipped back on post-Apr-26.
HACKATHON_AUDIT.md
HACKATHON_AUDIT_DETAILED.md
PROJECT_JOURNEY.md

# Plot artifacts under plots/ are gitignored (HF Space rejects binaries at the
# repo root). The README-rendered PNGs live under docs/assets/plots/ and are
# tracked normally — that path is not copied into the HF Docker image.
plots/*.png
plots/*.zip
plots/**/*.png
plots/**/*.zip
!docs/assets/plots/*.png
